title: Mr Boukadoum receives his Kuwaiti counterpart
text: The Minister of Foreign Affairs, Mr Sabri Boukadoum, received Wednesday at the headquarters of the ministry, his Kuwaiti counterpart, Sheikh Ahmed Nasser Al-Mohammed Al-Sabah, who is paying an official visit to Algeria.

The Kuwaiti Minister of Foreign Affairs, Special envoy of the Emir of Kuwait, Sheikh Nawaf Al-Ahmad Al-Jaber Al-Sabah, began an official visit to Algeria on Tuesday night to deliver a letter to the President of the Republic, Mr Abdelmadjid Tebboune.
